These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, onion, cranberry, broccoli
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, house, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, turkish, malaysian, american
4 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, turtle, lizard
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
 3. the spanish is on the left of the fan of house##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the turkish is the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the lizard and the fan of classical##2
10. the person eating pear is the owner of the lizard##1
11. the fan of house is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | cranberry  | pear    | broccoli    | onion   |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | dubstep   | house       | classical    |
| Nationality   | turkish | spanish | american    | malaysian |
| Pet           | ferret | lizard       | pony | turtle     |

