.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, banana, blueberry, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, traveling, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, rugby, cricket
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 2. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the person eating banana is the dutch##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 6. the dutch is on the left or right of the italian##3
 7. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 9. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
11. the italian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | grapes  | banana    | blueberry     | peach       |
| Hobby         | traveling | dancing | sudoku   | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | italian | dutch   | indonesian   | brazilian    |
| Sport         | rugby | cricket  | skiing | snowboarding   |

