.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, almond-milk, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, security-guard, videographer, analyst
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, polish, canadian, argentine
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, cat
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 2. the polish is the videographer##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the analyst##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the argentine##1
 8. the analyst is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | almond-milk   | 7up    | tea      |
| Job           | videographer | doctor | security-guard | analyst     |
| Nationality   | polish      | argentine   | malaysian   | canadian |
| Pet           | cat         | bird       | frog  | fish       |

