.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, cola, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: tomato, raspberry, pineapple, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, hiking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, water-polo, cricket
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating tomato##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the person drinking cola is the person eating cucumber##1
12. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | cola   | mirinda   | coffee   |
| Food       | raspberry        | cucumber | tomato    | pineapple       |
| Hobby      | cooking | collecting    | hiking  | puzzles |
| Sport      | swimming  | water-polo  | soccer | cricket    |

