.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, apple, banana, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, traveling, photography, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, social-worker, electrician, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, parkour, golf
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person eating papaya##2
 3. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the social-worker is the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the journalist is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating apple is the journalist##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is the social-worker##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
10. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | banana    | papaya      | pomegranate          | apple    |
| Hobby   | traveling | reading       | photography | writing |
| Job     | firefighter     | electrician      | social-worker     | journalist |
| Sport   | rugby   | golf | parkour        | rowing   |

