.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, cola, sprite
There 4 different types of food: spinach, peas, lettuce, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, jazz, soul, country
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, polish, australian
 1. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 5. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of country is between the polish and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the fan of soul is the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the italian is on the far right##1
10. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola  | fanta    | coffee       | sprite       |
| Food          | papaya    | lettuce | peas | spinach     |
| Music-Genre   | disco | soul        | country    | jazz   |
| Nationality   | dutch  | polish      | australian    | italian |

