4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, hedgehog, hamster
 1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the german is on the right of the japanese##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the owner of the frog is between the pakistani and the person watching romance movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
