 6. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking water##1
10. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

