 3. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the scientist##2
 5. the person eating lime is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 9. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
12. the analyst is on the left or right of the writer##3
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

