 3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite       | almond-milk | soy-milk        | iced-tea        |
| Hobby         | drawing | baking       | board-games | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | scientific        | action    | zombie      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey     | rugby    | cricket | parkour   |

