.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, reggae, country
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, american, russian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, golf, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, train, tram, van
 1. the fan of country is the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is between the nigerian and the turkish##2
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the american##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the fan of electronic is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the turkish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
10. the nigerian is in an even position##4
11. the nigerian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | salsa | country     | reggae        |
| Nationality   | russian | turkish  | american     | nigerian |
| Sport         | biathlon    | basketball | golf      | tennis |
| Transport     | van | train     | tram | trike       |

 